    "Following growth at 37 °C and 250 r.p.m.",
    "for 2 h, cultures were induced with 100 μl of an LB medium solution containing appropriate antibiotics and the inducer molecule dissolved in 10 μl DMSO.",
    "Cultures were grown for an additional 4 h at 37 °C and 250 r.p.m.",
    "and subsequently centrifuged (3500 × g, 4 °C, 10 min).",
    "Supernatant was removed, and cell pellets were resuspended in 1 ml PBS."
